reviews.review_text: One Hell of a Show I was at this show. The energy was amazing then and it's nice to feel it come through the recording. I closed my eyes and listened to the whole show. Talk about the crest of a wave...I felt like I was there again. Oh man, those were the days. Terrapin>drums>space>darkstar??? does it get any better? Not in my memory. I saw a total of three shows that played darkstar and terrapin in the same show and they are all emblazzoned in my memory.
